      <_description>Possible values: 'none' - do not store href in the plain text; 'inline' - show href beside the text link, like: "label &lt;href&gt;"; 'reference' - show href as reference to the end of the text, like: "label [1] ...... [1] label href"; 'reference-without-label' - show href as reference to the end of the text without label, like: "label [1] ...... [1] href"</_description>
